4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals without prior knowledge aiming to become cybersecurity specialists. The program spans 16 weeks with three live online classes each week, accommodating up to 16 students per class. Participants will acquire a robust foundation in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, along with essential skills in cloud security, penetration testing, and risk management. Graduates receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, recognized by various institutions. Classes are available in English and Spanish. For further details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop